                "description": "Diagram of an artificial neuron j. Inputs x0=1 (bias), x1, x2, x3, ..., xn are connected to a summation node Σ via weights w0j, w1j, w2j, w3j, ..., wnj. The weighted sum vj is passed to an activation function f to produce the output yj.",
